<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Chis čs achukma, Chis čs achukma
 Chis čs  čt achukm čshke;
 Chis čs  čt h čpiŐĪ hullo hosh
 Pi  člhtob čt illi tok:
 Yakoke, ahnit e talowa.

[V2]
 Hatak ilb čsha, hatak ilb čsha
 Fehna h čpia hoke;
 Chis čs im anumpa hoka
 Akob čffi pia hosh,
 Pi yoshoba okpulo yoke.

[V3]
 Y čmohmi hoka himak ok čno,
 Il ayoshoba tok aŐĪ
 Kanchit e taiyahlikbano,
 Il aiahni fehna hosh,
 Yakoht e talohoŐĪwa hoke.

[V4]
 ChuŐĪk čsh himona, chuŐĪk čsh achukma,
 ChuŐĪk čsh ai aŐĪhli fehna
 Chis čs il im asilhhakma,
 Et pihiŐĪma hi oke;
 AŐĪhli fehna kil im asilhha.

[V5]
 Nitak kanima, nitak kil ahno,
 Nitak hopahki keyu,
 Pilli pulla chiŐĪ mak oke;
 Chis čs iŐĪ yimmi  čto
 NaŐĪ yuhuŐĪkpa na bilia he.</lyrics>
